%% Dark-launch comparison. See 06-dark-launch-strategy.md
flowchart TB
  Get[redis.get key] --> DL{TENANCY_DARK_LAUNCH?}
  DL -- off --> Normal[return scopeKey read]
  DL -- on --> Pair[compareLegacyAndTenantKey]
  Pair --> Both[read legacy AND tenant values]
  Both --> Classify[classifyMismatch]
  Classify --> Type{mismatch?}
  Type -- none --> OkTally[summary.ok++]
  Type -- missing/stale/serialization/value --> Report[recordTenantEvent dark-launch-mismatch - keyFamily + tenant + type, NO values]
  OkTally --> Ret[RETURN legacy value - response unchanged]
  Report --> Ret
